snippet.title: Cosminers  - Official Reveal Trailer - Wishlist on Steam ⭐
snippet.description:
⭐Wishlist Cosminers on Steam:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1690100/Cosminers/?utm_source=youtube&utm_campaign=trailer&utm_content=announcement

This is our official reveal trailer of Cosminers!
A unique game that combines elements such as:
🚀 survival
🔧 simulator
👾 tower defense
🔫 fps
🧱 base building
💎 resource management
☠️ roguelike

⚡️ Follow us for Cosminers updates: 
Discord: https://discord.gg/cosminers
Reddit: https://www.reddit.com/r/Cosminers/
X: https://twitter.com/Cosminers
Facebook: https://facebook.com/Cosminers
Website: http://cosminers.com/
